{"tid":1354230,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真post] 逆轉呢場運動嘅機會嚟啦","createTime":"2019-07-23T05:59:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T06:07:02.000Z","uid":200799,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f6a7709c64089daa935ea3e50a25df3560a73ae8","tid":1354230,"uid":200799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:59:49.000Z","msg":"一直以來民眾都冇實質嘅談判條件<br />\n係因為缺乏有組織嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">武裝力量</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n然而，經過呢次元朗黑幫劈友<br />\n我哋大可以仿效大埔咁樣組成自己嘅人民自衛隊<br />\n係每一區都有一定嘅軍事力量<br />\n<br />\n而最重要嘅係今次嘅組成係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">出師有名</span></span></strong><br />\n因為警察切切實實已經唔能夠保護人民<br />\n我哋要借助元朗事件嘅輿論力量 擴展人民自衛隊嘅範圍<br />\n<br />\n當18區都有一定嘅力量嘅時候<br />\n極權政府亦難以打擊 完全可以Be water<br />\n區與區之間又可以互相策應<br />\n<br />\n只要時機一到 天下有變<br />\n集合18區嘅力量討伐金鐘同埋西環<br />\n全面推翻政府<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562f0b56abcfd09030ee2c49428b05d38f4d8922","tid":1354230,"uid":200799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:00:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e919fa53f9a0de308f52fad209f5a61af9092634","tid":1354230,"uid":200799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:00:19.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"de2ed87a05897710ea4fde081b9048d93f8d587e","tid":1354230,"uid":200799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:02:10.000Z","msg":"咁樣同時亦係有大台 同埋冇大台嘅狀態<br />\n聯邦自治 再集結成為一股力量 <br />\n推翻極權"},{"pid":"c3ce6f585f3567faa1cb8c7b5b529912a6c18936","tid":1354230,"uid":200799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:02:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"50b5f1fa7e5f0bb0bc3c84d2c410213fe315ef74","tid":1354230,"uid":200799,"like